Amendment No. 1 to Senate Bill 269
Amend Senate Bill 269 as originally introduced:
Page 1, line 36, delete "primary or branch office" and substitute "primary
office, satellite office, or alternate delivery site"
AND
Page 2, line 2, delete "(2)(A)" and substitute "(2)"
AND
Page 2, delete lines 3 through 8, and substitute the following:
"provide notification to the Department of Health and the Health Services
Permit Agency forty-five (45) days in advance of adding an office location
from which the home health services agency or hospice agency plans to serve
within a one-hundred-mile area of the new location."
